-- tf.h3: How to create custom component, using default attributes?

`FTD` lang is flexible and you can define your custom names to the default component.
Below example shows usage of custom name:

-- cb.code: `-- inbox` with custom name as e.g. `showcase`:
lang: ftd

\-- inbox.inbox showcase:
caption title:
body body: 
title: $title
body: $body





-- tf.markdown: 

How to use above custom name `-- showcase`:

-- cb.code: custom `-- showcase` usage:
lang: ftd

\-- showcase: This is your Title

Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do 
eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad 
minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut

